      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a paper for my history of science class about the eugenics movement in the early 1900s. I need to understand the specific logic they used to justify their racial hierarchies to write a proper analysis. Can you elaborate on the main arguments eugenicists used back then to claim certain races were superior or inferior to others?",
