      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense for the paper. To get into the specifics of their academic reasoning, how did they actually use concepts like biology or social Darwinism to prove these differences? Like, what kind of specific \"evidence\" or scientific-sounding justifications did they lean on to claim that certain groups were inherently more advanced or capable than others?",
